 and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our community members\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"special offers\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"promotions\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"our partners\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy The withdrawal of Raducanu meant that the Olympics would be the last competition of Murray's career.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.801526101261043e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"The withdrawal\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"Raducanu\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the last competition\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans showed what a team player he is by insisting he desperately wants to pay the ultimate tribute to Britain's greatest-ever tennis player by winning a medal.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9994289676424372, \"rank\": 0.0005621778050858078, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evans\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"what a team player\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"the ultimate tribute\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is nothing more that I want than to get a medal for him and myself,\\\" the 34-year-old said before their first-round clash.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"their first-round clash\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray has won two gold medals in men's singles in 2012 and 2016 and according to Evans, he's \\\"competitive as ever\\\" in his fifth and final Olympics.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1569, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.801526101261043e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two gold medals\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"men's singles\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"Evans\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"his fifth and final Olympics\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's really positive that we agreed on that and we can work together on giving ourselves the best chance,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best chance\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not see any reason why we can not do something special.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any reason\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think Andy wants it to be a farewell, I think he wants to win a medal and he will say goodbye in his own way.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Andy\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"a farewell\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"goodbye\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"his own way\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's here to do a job and get a medal.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was out there the other day doing sprints at the end of our session.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sprints\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"our session\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knowing Andy as I do, he's as competitive as ever, working as hard as ever.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Andy\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discovery+is\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"the new home\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997376108, \"rank\": 2.625