e\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's probably up there,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Pro\\u00adbably the way that we were playing to that stage would have not suggested that we were likely to come back.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pro\\u00adbably the way\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3282}, {\"ngram\": \"that stage\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I certainly did not feel like I was playing well.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evo played well at times but for both of us we can play much better than that.\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evo\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then it just all clicked at the end and we played some pretty, pretty good stuff.\\\"\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"some pretty, pretty good stuff\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH CONNECT WITH US TODAY'S PAPER See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3731, \"end\": 3744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.827898025086112e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SEARCH CONNECT\", \"from\": 35